{"tid":433714,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登正能量] 一人一個令你唔捨得離開呢個世界嘅理由","createTime":"2017-10-12T14:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T18:35:51.000Z","uid":83025,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e243d9b44f027adaadc450b6c23762743b324f87","tid":433714,"uid":83025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:42:48.000Z","msg":"無論係幾細、幾無聊、幾微不足道嘅原因都好，<br />\n喺呢個世界努力地生存緊嘅大家一定有值得自己留戀嘅事物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不妨喺呢度分享下，鼓勵同提醒大家世界仲有好多美好嘅事物值得我地珍惜同生存落去。<br />\n<br />\n我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想為左令世界變得好少少出一分力(幾細微嘅事都好)、仲有好多好靚嘅風景想睇、地方想去、好多野想做。<br />\n<br />\n難得黎到，唔想人生Online毫無意義就完左。<br />\n就算所有野到最後會變成虛無，都想喺世界留低少少屬於自己嘅痕跡。<br />\n<br />\n諗到再補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8354792366902d492c7b48792347da0ab7f3a71f","tid":433714,"uid":6883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:43:12.000Z","msg":"怕痛"},{"pid":"ff715ae096f1152176c1273705291689235f9d35","tid":433714,"uid":6883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:43:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>怕痛</blockquote><br />\n之外無嚕"},{"pid":"fb435690d74ea241a81cc14cac3d2a8014e2a9e7","tid":433714,"uid":80176,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:43:55.000Z","msg":"難得有條大賓周， 死咗就冇架啦"},{"pid":"9e05a875391a87818e051d46e7f01bf6213fa3f4","tid":433714,"uid":115452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:44:34.000Z","msg":"愛情<br />\n好耐冇拍過拖了<br />\n狗仔<br />\n去旅行"},{"pid":"3f13be2ff5ea48a92fef4bde9c96bbc4b9306e79","tid":433714,"uid":150706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:45:09.000Z","msg":"hunter hunter未完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623fb7eeaabfa59854d058113db19efa06efb3d6","tid":433714,"uid":1